Title: Herald Validation Rule Catalog
Version: 2026.2.2
Maintainer: Vignesh <vthanik@users.noreply.github.com>
License: MIT
URL: https://github.com/vthanik/heraldrules

Description:
  Source-of-truth rule catalog for the herald R package.
  Contains 3,593 regulatory validation rules (YAML/JSON) covering
  CDISC conformance, FDA Business and Validator rules, PMDA rules,
  NCI EVS controlled terminology, and Herald-original gap-fill rules.

  This is NOT an R package. It is a versioned rule catalog:
    1. Rules are authored and validated here (see tests/)
    2. Quarterly refreshes run via inst/scripts/refresh-all.R
    3. At herald release time, copy into herald/inst/rules/:
         cp -r engines configs ct manifest.json ../herald/inst/rules/

Engines:
  cdisc/     450 rules  CDISC Library conformance rules
  fda/       660 rules  FDA Business Rules v1.5 + Validator Rules v1.6
  pmda/    1,041 rules  PMDA Validation Rules v6.0
  ct/      1,210 rules  Per-codelist controlled terminology rules
  herald/    232 rules  Herald gap-fill and hardcoded spec checks
